Package com.github.basking2.sdsai.io

Class LazyFileOutputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • com.github.basking2.sdsai.io.LazyOutputStream
        • com.github.basking2.sdsai.io.LazyFileOutputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.io.Flushable, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    public class LazyFileOutputStream
extends LazyOutputStream
    A lazy file output stream delays opening a file to write until its internal buffer is filled. This is a form of buffered output stream in which not only are writes delayed, but also the file opening.
